16	 * Inspector parameter renderers — spec §13.
17	 *
18	 * Read-only field panels per element kind. The Apply / Reset footer is
19	 * left to the controlling Inspector component (which only shows it when
20	 * dirty=true). Numeric writes through the engine command pipeline land
21	 * separately when the redesigned palette gains drawing flow.
